===Noun===
'''acinus''' (plural acini)

# (Bot.) One of the small grains or [[drupelets]] which make up some kinds of [[fruit]], as the [[blackberry]], [[raspberry]], etc.
# (Bot.) A [[grapestone]].
# (Anat.) One of the granular masses which constitute a [[racemose]] or compound [[gland]], as the [[pancreas]]; also, one of the [[saccular]] [[recesses]] in the [[lobules]] of a racemose gland. [[Quain]].

====Etymology====
Latin [[grape]], [[grapestone]].